OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776258665
OL,3,CRory McIlroy wins back-to-back Masters
OL,5,FNorthern Ireland's Rory McIlroy has
OL,6,Fwon the Masters for the second year in
OL,7,Fa row.
OL,9,FThe Holywood star became only the
OL,10,Ffourth man to win back-to-back Masters
OL,11,Fafter watching a number of challengers
OL,12,Frise and fall before taking control on
OL,13,Fthe back nine to win by a shot.
OL,15,FRory played out a final round of 71,
OL,16,Fone under and 12 under overall, one
OL,17,Fahead of Scottie Scheffler.
OL,19,FThere was emotional scenes at the 18th
OL,20,Fin Augusta as Rory got hugs from mum
OL,21,FRosie and dad Gerry.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
