OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776258665
OL,3,CRory McIlroy wins back-to-back Masters
OL,5,F"I can't believe I waited 17 years to
OL,6,Fget one green jacket and I get two in
OL,7,Fa row," he said.
OL,9,F"All my perseverance finally paid off."
OL,11,FHe said his final round felt 'pretty
OL,12,Fsimilar to the last year's. He said he
OL,13,Fwas 'so glad' his mother and father
OL,14,Fgot to be at Augusta this year having
OL,15,Fmissed last year's triumph, saying
OL,16,Fthey would enjoy the moment together.
OL,18,F"It's only the second major win my
OL,19,Fmum's been at, she was at The Open in
OL,20,FHoylake in 2014," he said.
OL,26,@zD@AOU|D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776258665
OL,3,CRory McIlroy wins back-to-back Masters
OL,5,F"There was a piece of them that didn't
OL,6,Fwant to come this year after not being
OL,7,Fhere last year but I'm so glad they
OL,8,Fgot to experience this today."
OL,10,FStruggling to contain his emotions, he
OL,11,Fadded: "Thanks you for all the
OL,12,Fsupport, I was a little kid with a
OL,13,Fdream.
OL,15,F"I had amazing support from back home
OL,16,Fand I can't thank the all back home
OL,17,Fenough."
OL,26,@mD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/12
