PN,44804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776258665
OL,3,CRory McIlroy wins back-to-back Masters
OL,5,FThe Northern Irishman joined Jack
OL,6,FNicklaus (1965 and 1996), Sir Nick
OL,7,FFaldo (1989 and 1990) and Tiger Woods
OL,8,F(2001 and 2002) in an elite club of
OL,9,Fplayers to successfully defend their
OL,10,Ftitle at Augusta National.
OL,12,FA year ago he needed a play-off to
OL,13,Fcomplete the career grand slam after
OL,14,Fbogeying the last, beating Justin Rose
OL,15,Fat the first extra hole.
OL,17,FBut having ridden through a scratchy
OL,18,Fopening six holes where he fell two
OL,19,Fbehind he rediscovered the control
OL,20,Fwhich had seen him open up a six-shot
OL,21,F36-hole advantage.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776258665
OL,3,CRory McIlroy wins back-to-back Masters
OL,5,FTyrrell Hatton, who shot a 66 to get
OL,6,Fto 10 under, and two-time champion
OL,7,FScottie Scheffler, who after 12
OL,8,Fsuccessive pars birdied 15 and 16 to
OL,9,Fappear over McIlroy's shoulder, left
OL,10,Fit too late in getting to 11 under
OL,11,Fwith a 68 to exert any significant
OL,12,Fpressure.
OL,14,FRose, with whom the tussle had again
OL,15,Fbeen the tightest at the peak of the
OL,16,Fbattle, stumbled around Amen Corner to
OL,17,Flet his slender lead slip and took too
OL,18,Flong to recover with a bogey ending
OL,19,Fhis challenge at 17 as he finished
OL,20,Fwith a 70 to join the group on 10
OL,21,Funder.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776258665
OL,3,CRory McIlroy wins back-to-back Masters
OL,5,FMcIlroy, learning the lessons from
OL,6,Flast year, was in no mood to make any
OL,7,Fmistakes and parred his way through
OL,8,Fthe next four holes to reach the last
OL,9,Fwith a two-shot cushion.
OL,11,FBut there was still time for some late
OL,12,Fdrama as, in keeping with his driving
OL,13,Fthis week, he took one final trip to
OL,14,Fthe Georgia pines down the right and
OL,15,Fhad to effect a slinging hook into the
OL,16,Ffront bunker.
OL,18,FHe splashed out to 15ft and two-putted
OL,19,Fto pick up a second green jacket with
OL,20,Fa final-round 71 for a 12-under total.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776258665
OL,3,CRory McIlroy wins back-to-back Masters
OL,5,FMcIlroy was misty-eyed but there were
OL,6,Fnot the tears and emotional release of
OL,7,Fa year ago and he was able to enjoy
OL,8,Fthe moment with his family at the back
OL,9,Fof the 18th green.
OL,11,FThe foundations had been laid over the
OL,12,Ffirst two days but the hard work was
OL,13,Fdone over the weekend as rounds of 73-
OL,14,F71 showed the pressure he was put
OL,15,Funder but was still able to come out
OL,16,Fsmiling.
OL,18,FHis resurgence started with back-to-
OL,19,Fback birdies at the seventh and eighth
OL,20,Fto put him within a shot of Rose, two
OL,21,Fgroups ahead on 12 under.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776258665
OL,3,CRory McIlroy wins back-to-back Masters
OL,5,FBut the pivotal period came around
OL,6,FAmen Corner, which had cost him so
OL,7,Fdearly on Saturday and played a large
OL,8,Fpart in him surrendering an overnight
OL,9,Fsix-shot lead.
OL,11,FLast year the 11th was where Rose
OL,12,Fbegan his back-nine birdie charge on
OL,13,Fhis way to a 66 but this time the
OL,14,FEnglishman fell foul of the toughest
OL,15,Fhole on the course, missing the green
OL,16,Fto the right to drop back alongside
OL,17,FMcIlroy on 11 under.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776258665
OL,3,CRory McIlroy wins back-to-back Masters
OL,5,FAnother missed green resulted in a
OL,6,Fsecond successive bogey to hand the
OL,7,Foutright lead back to McIlroy, who
OL,8,Flearned his lesson from the previous
OL,9,Fday by ensuring he avoided the pond on
OL,10,F11.
OL,12,FAnd then things turned in the space of
OL,13,Fa couple of minutes just before 5.30pm
OL,14,Flocal time.
OL,16,FMcIlroy's brilliant approach to the
OL,17,Fshort 12th finished seven feet from
OL,18,Fthe pin for his fourth birdie of the
OL,19,Fafternoon.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
