PN,44810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776258665
OL,3,CRory McIlroy wins back-to-back Masters
OL,5,FRose, meanwhile, had been looking at a
OL,6,Fpotential eagle after hitting his
OL,7,Fsecond to 30ft at the par-five 13th,
OL,8,Fonly to race his attempt eight feet
OL,9,Fpast and then, to compound the error,
OL,10,Fmissed the returning birdie putt.
OL,12,FThat meant Mcllroy was two clear with
OL,13,Ftwo par fives still to play and he
OL,14,Ftook advantage of the first, the 13th
OL,15,Fwhich double-bogeyed in his final
OL,16,Fround 12 months ago, to move three
OL,17,Fclear.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776258665
OL,3,CRory McIlroy wins back-to-back Masters
OL,5,FRose birdied the 15th to reduce the
OL,6,Fgap to two and he was joined by two-
OL,7,Ftime champion Scottie Scheffler, who
OL,8,Fafter 12 successive pars, produced
OL,9,Fback-to-back birdies to move into
OL,10,Fcontention but neither had the final
OL,11,Fflourish.
OL,13,FMcIlroy almost had his 'Tiger' moment
OL,14,Fat the 16th having gone through the
OL,15,Fback fringe. Putting, where Woods
OL,16,Fchipped, the ball went at right angles
OL,17,Fdown the slope to nestle next to the
OL,18,Fhole.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
